reviewText: Didn't keep my daughter's attention, they start out with 4 digit adding - which is probably okay for a 2nd grader and maybe even a first grader but they don't really teach it so much as do it in front of you on 'paper' - the puppets are more of a distraction - the production value is decent but this fell flat for us - team umizoomi has more educational value for keeping the attention of the person watching. The last thing you want is to trap a kid with boring curriculum.
